Stock Picks Global Logistics Has Steak in China’s Growth China’s appetite for online deliveries, better meat refrigeration a boon for this Singapore logistics stock. By Daniel Shane July 23, 2015 8:26 p.m. ET 
Logistics companies are among the most obvious benefactors of China’s explosive e-commerce growth and the increasing hordes who order things online, but investors should also chew over another trend supporting logistics stocks: China’s rising appetite for frozen food.
